{"tid":2241530,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"武漢肺炎｜紐約近百年歷史羅斯福酒店 敵不過疫情將結束營業","createTime":"2020-10-13T11:11:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-13T11:20:19.000Z","uid":293494,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"44eb875887582a7ae84d75994bc0e36e006157de","tid":2241530,"uid":293494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T11:11:38.000Z","msg":"//美國酒店住宿協會（AHLA）和數百名業界高層上月致函國會，促請當局協助業界解決前所未有的財務困難。該協會主席兼行政總裁羅哲斯（Chip Rogers）指，「旅遊需求創紀錄新低，有成千上萬間酒店無力支付商業抵押貸款，並且面臨不得不永久關閉殘酷現實」，他又說，「成千上萬的酒店員工將失去工作，依靠這些酒店推動當地旅遊業的小型企業，也可能會面臨類似的命運。」<br />\n<br />\n該組織引用美國物業研究機構Trepp的一份報告，截至7月，美國有23.4％酒店拖欠債務近30日，去年同期只有1.3％，反映酒店還款能力愈來愈低。報告又指，休斯敦有66%酒店涉拖欠債務，是全美大城市中比率最高的地方，其次是芝加哥有53.8％、紐約有38.7％、西雅圖有36.1％和奧斯汀有35.7％。//<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20201013/RAQLLIOGBZFNRBEHQ3QSFUFHNQ/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR2xR0_lxjKuNLRluKawiJtpCPkIrk1t8K1e4F1WBg_lDfjfmTq2STirlaQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20201013%2FRAQLLIOGBZFNRBEHQ3QSFUFHNQ%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR2xR0_lxjKuNLRluKawiJtpCPkIrk1t8K1e4F1WBg_lDfjfmTq2STirlaQ&d=uoj2XAvVwhv3g67ADWIJbZbpPLVkgxcsq72qYZiHPFQ%3D&h=05b18770\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20201013%2FRAQLLIOGBZFNRBEHQ3QSFUFHNQ%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR2xR0_lxjKuNLRluKawiJtpCPkIrk1t8K1e4F1WBg_lDfjfmTq2STirlaQ&h=cd999ed3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20201013/RAQLLIOGBZFNRBEHQ3QSFUFHNQ/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR2xR0_lxjKuNLRluKawiJtpCPkIrk1t8K1e4F1WBg_lDfjfmTq2STirlaQ</a>"},{"pid":"f0fa62a26637e803f4f661e3b07e526c37a663ed","tid":2241530,"uid":293494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"44eb875887582a7ae84d75994bc0e36e006157de","tid":2241530,"uid":293494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T11:11:38.000Z","msg":"//美國酒店住宿協會（AHLA）和數百名業界高層上月致函國會，促請當局協助業界解決前所未有的財務困難。該協會主席兼行政總裁羅哲斯（Chip Rogers）指，「旅遊需求創紀錄新低，有成千上萬間酒店無力支付商業抵押貸款，並且面臨不得不永久關閉殘酷現實」，他又說，「成千上萬的酒店員工將失去工作，依靠這些酒店推動當地旅遊業的小型企業，也可能會面臨類似的命運。」<br />\n<br />\n該組織引用美國物業研究機構Trepp的一份報告，截至7月，美國有23.4％酒店拖欠債務近30日，去年同期只有1.3％，反映酒店還款能力愈來愈低。報告又指，休斯敦有66%酒店涉拖欠債務，是全美大城市中比率最高的地方，其次是芝加哥有53.8％、紐約有38.7％、西雅圖有36.1％和奧斯汀有35.7％。//<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20201013/RAQLLIOGBZFNRBEHQ3QSFUFHNQ/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR2xR0_lxjKuNLRluKawiJtpCPkIrk1t8K1e4F1WBg_lDfjfmTq2STirlaQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20201013%2FRAQLLIOGBZFNRBEHQ3QSFUFHNQ%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR2xR0_lxjKuNLRluKawiJtpCPkIrk1t8K1e4F1WBg_lDfjfmTq2STirlaQ&d=uoj2XAvVwhv3g67ADWIJbZbpPLVkgxcsq72qYZiHPFQ%3D&h=05b18770\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20201013%2FRAQLLIOGBZFNRBEHQ3QSFUFHNQ%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR2xR0_lxjKuNLRluKawiJtpCPkIrk1t8K1e4F1WBg_lDfjfmTq2STirlaQ&h=cd999ed3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20201013/RAQLLIOGBZFNRBEHQ3QSFUFHNQ/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR2xR0_lxjKuNLRluKawiJtpCPkIrk1t8K1e4F1WBg_lDfjfmTq2STirlaQ</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T11:12: